<reference id="Application_Server_Resources_74" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Menu Options and User Roles</title>
    <refbody>
        <section>
            <p>This appendix provides an overview of the user roles required for using the menu options at the <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> administration portal which are of relevance to a technology provider. For details on the menu options, refer to the <i>Online Help</i>.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Account Menu</title>
            <p>The following user roles are required for using the menu options in the <b>Account</b> menu:</p>
            <table colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
                <tgroup cols="2">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="196.5pt"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="282.75pt"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"><b>Edit profile</b>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Any user role</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry><b>Import users</b><p>(if the organization uses LDAP-based user authentication)</p></entry>
                            <entry>Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"
                                    ><b>Change password</b><p>(if the organization does not use an external system for user authentication)</p></entry>
                            <entry colname="col2"
                                >Any user role</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"><b>Register new users</b></entry>
                            <entry colname="col2"
                                >Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"><b>Manage users</b>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry><b>LDAP settings</b><p>(if the organization uses LDAP-based user authentication)</p></entry>
                            <entry>Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"><b>Create report</b>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"><b>Process triggers</b>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Administrator</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1"
                                ><b>Manage processes</b><p>(if the organization is connected to an external process control system)</p></entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Any user role</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <b>Manage suppliers</b>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">Technology manager</entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </section>
        <section>
